<br>
The arguments again- Highlander cloth casters - they have too much str and con.<br>
<br>
The argument for- they have the same stats as a Norseman, who can bea  cloth caster. Dammit, even a Troll (100 str) can be a cloth caster!<br>
<br>
Friars- The Highlander is too tough? (surely there are Scottish vigilante ninjas out there... maybe Fingoniel can shed some light on this <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  )<br>
<br>
Argument for - The 'overpowering' thing about a Friar is his staff damage- based on all Dexterity. So a Highlander Friar would be doing less damage than a Briton one. A Saracen friar, now THAT would be a mistake.<br>
<br>
Highlander infiltrators- arguments against- Scots are too honourable. Yeah right, my best buddy is a Scot by birth, and, OK, this one time he took a... well, never mind <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  Damage-wise, theoretically a Highlander Thrust inf would have the best damage.<br>
<br>
He would, of course, evade a fair bit less, and hit a fair bit slower. No triple- Hamstrings for you, Hamish.<br>
<br>
Saracen Clerics- argument against - they are heathens(sp?) . Sorry, we've already converted them to zealot Paladins, why can't they be ordained? Anyway their Con/Str is pretty low so it's not like they'll be war machines.<br>
<br>
Avelonian Friars - How nerfworthy could they be, seriously? <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Avelonian Infs and Scouts - I just don't see the argument against this. Surely their points in Int are wasted, if anything. Their Quick is very nice, but it's not gonna add overpowering hefty damage.<br>
<br>
Lurikeens can become Rangers and they have massive Quickness like the Avvy, allowing them to fire longbows (or the equiv.) at 1.5second speeds, or near. Let's see some Mr Spock style snipers. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=demised>Demised</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br>  Posts: 46<br> <font color=#000000>(7/15/03 7:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=71.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: let's open the esthetic box! How groovy would this be--</span><hr size=1> At the moment... ALL Avalonians besides a select few are casters... Every caster I see almost is Avalonian... &quot;Group sends, &quot;We have a caster incoming&quot; $20 says he/she is Avalonian...<br>
